reviewText: Don't know. It was a gift for a neighbor. No response so far.
Just ok. Not great sound or picture quality
I gave as a Christmas gift.  The recipient is a music lover. He said it was OK but too much "behind the scenes" which broke the charm of an inspriational concert.
I was sorely disappointed in this.  It is NOT a concert>  It is more like they were trying to make a movie, which turned out badly.
My mother loves it. What else can I say but Thank you for keeping your price low.
Used this DVD on taking a trip to see Vienna boys Choir in person in Springfield Mass. Was a great video
Yes beautiful music coming from usual Vienna Boy's Choir voices. As far as it being a story or theme,it was lacking in that area. It would have been better if it were a concert/recital!
quick and good, i buy it for my friends, so we will see how it works. i hope my friend will like it, i can not write down too much detail because i didn't open it yet.
